properties.text:
A voice booms out:
Welcome traveller...

It's been many years
since i had any guests

Please, let yourself in
and rest. you must 
be weary

I forgot to mention.
I like puzzles.

Some of them are easy...

The bridge crumbles
away behind you,
leaving you trapped

You must venture inside
and find another way
to get home

But if you solve them all
you will be rewarded

I'm afraid my garden
has become quite
overgrown recently

This part of the castle 
is in dire need of repair

Watch your step
